Job Description 4 : 

- 7+ of years’ experience with at least 2 years of operations engineering experience as a lead. 
- Have experience dealing with competing priorities and setting right expectations with stakeholders 
- AWS expert with a solid command of abstractions / services such as IAM, VPCs, Route53, and Terraform (CloudFormation) 
- Have experience with EKS and understand how to leverage it securely 
- Comfortable working as part of a hands-on team to collaborate on designs, implementation, tuning and support of our systems 
- Has strong experience as a professional technologist working with a distributed team 
- Passionately measure system performance and scalability 
- Are not dogmatic in your technology choices, but have the passion and knowledge to engage in debates about various tooling and technologies 
- Are interested in building a reliable, fault-tolerant, multi-tenant platform and delivering it to a global user base 
- Know how to scale yourself through scripting & automation and ultimately through mentoring & team leadership 
- Knowledge of spring boot web services, Java is also a plus

