Job Description 6 :

Responsibilities:

- Responsible for the design and implementation of Secure and Scalable Infrastructure.
- Own and automate infrastructure provisioning, demand forecasting, and capacity planning.
- Build automation tools and frameworks to improve the system's observability, availability, reliability, performance/latency, and monitoring.
- The monitoring system, application health, security controls, and cost.
- Practice sustainable incident response as well as participate in peer reviews and blameless postmortems.
- Envision, implement, and rollout the best DevOps tooling and automation for all of our services.
- Build and maintain CI/CD pipelines.


Requirements:

- Expertise in any one of AWS/Azure/GCP.
- Strong working knowledge of Kubernetes.
- Strong Experience with infrastructure automation tools like Terraform/Pulumi/Cloudformation, etc.
- Strong debugging/troubleshooting skills.
- Deep working knowledge of Linux servers and networking.

