- Experience in automating large scale developments with deployment management systems: Puppet, Chef, CFEngine, Capistrano or a similar system
- Experience carrying out monitoring and performance metrics analysis using one of the following tools: Hyperic, Prometheus, Nagios, Cacti, Munin, Ganglia or a similar program
- AWS/EC2 experience
- Must have Linux experience (preferably Ubuntu, Red Hat or CentOS)
- Apache Tomcat and HTTP Server experience
- Good understanding of Java deployment
- Administration and support of public data center solutions provided by AWS
- Administration and support of Container Orchestration Tools like Docker/ Kubernetes/ Openshift
- Developing using infrastructure automation solutions using tools like : Ansible/ Puppet/ Chef/ Terraform
- Administration and support of managing queue solutions: Kafka/Pulsar
- Administration and support of Gitlab/ Github/ SVN/ Subversion/ Bitbucket

